racters for \"诲1\".<br>(1) Teaching; instruction.<br>(2) Words of advice and advice.<br>(3) Seduction. See \"Teaching Fortune-telling Thieves\".<br>(4) Through \"regret\". repentance.<br>instruct<br>English translation of words<br>◎ 诲<br>instruct, teach<br>instruct<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[You Ji 1] [Words Department] 　诲; Kangxi strokes: 14; Page number: page 1188 to 18<br>[Ancient text]? [Tang Yun] Rhyme within the barren cut [Jiyun] [Rhyme will] call within the cut [Zhengyun] call on the opposite cut,? The sound is dark. [Said the text] Xiao Qiao also. [Xu Yue] Ding Ning tells it, if it is too obscure. [Jade articles] Instruction also. [Guang Yun] Education training. [Yi·Ci] Slowly hides and stalks, sulls the content and slanders. 【Book·Fate】Gathering in the morning and evening, to assist Taiwan's Germany. 【Poetry·Xiaoya】Educational son, Shigu resembles it.　Yehuo and cut, sound. [Poetry·Daya] The bandits, the bandits, the Shi Weifu Temple.　 Ye Xuyi cut again, hope to go. [Qin·Taishan Carved Stones] Suspense night sleep, build Changli, and specialize in longing. The scriptures are preached, far and near, and the sacred aspirations are inherited. Three sentences into rhyme. 【Wu Ji·Rhyme Replenishment】Gu Weiyun and Zhitong. Textual research: [[Book·Said Fate] Supplementing Wang De in the morning and evening. 〕 　 I would like to change from Wang De to Tai De according to the original text.<br>instruct<br>Source glyph<br>instruct<br>Name meaning<br>Means to teach, to teach.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274319866384.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274319866384.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148274319866384.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">诲<br>形声字。言(i)表意,表示用言语教导;晦(hui )省声,晦有昏暗义,表示使受教海者从昏暗中明白事理。形旁简化。<br>本义是教导。<br>教导:教~「训~|~人不倦。<br>~人不倦 ~淫~盜 教~ 训~<br>huì<br>議<br>誨誨诲<br>金<br>隶<br>五,; 